        <mxCell id="dL4lOMw5zDBnu7NahARo-13" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;" value="Output will consist of:&lt;div&gt;- The Yamada OBright&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;yamada.obright-V1@3.0-service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;- The .rc&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;init.yamada.obright.rc&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Later will be put on vendor/&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;And the OBright will given fs context to write to brightness&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
